text: 3 bed, 1 bath home tucked away on a dead end private cul de sac, backs to privacy with trees and greenbelt. 3 bed 1 bath home ready for you to move in and put your on design spin on it. Welcome to this 5-acre lifestyle property offering endless possibilities! This charming 1910 two-story farmhouse features a cozy propane fireplace, mini-split heating & cooling, and natural light throughout. Perfect for equestrian enthusiasts, with a 3-stall horse barn, outdoor arena, all-weather lunging pad, and well-draining pastures. Aviation lovers will appreciate the private airplane hangar and access to Meadow Mist Airfield. The spacious shop w/ insulated room, automatic generator, and serene surroundings make it ideal for event hosting, hobby farming, flower farming, or creating your dream retreat. Imagine hosting weddings, retreats, or turning the land into a thriving dahlia farm. A rare find just minutes from Bellingham & Lynden!

Welcome to your charming new home in the desirable Birchwood neighborhood! Dont miss this perfect blend of charm and convenience!

text: Discover modern living at Darby Estates Condominiums in the coveted Cordata neighborhood! This spacious, ground-level unit offers 2 large bedrooms, each with ensuite bathrooms, new contemporary lighting, and walk-in closets. The kitchen impresses with stainless steel appliances, generous counter space, and ample cabinetry, plus a separate laundry room with a washer/dryer. Endless storage and pantry. Includes some virtually staged photos.

text: Great Central Location, home and lot! Take a look at this cute 2 bedroom craftsman home on a .95 flat sunny lot. This home has been tastefully updated with a newer kitchen and bathroom. Fresh paint on the inside makes it ready to move in! Newer furnace as well as a pellet stove in both the home and shop. Enjoy the back covered patio or stay out of the rain in the back sunroom. There is a spacious detached garage with room for 1-2 cars or shop space, plus shop space behind the and a one car carport. Also room on this lot to add a mega shop in the back NE corner! new 3 bedroom septic.Great option to expand or add an attached ADU. Sale includes both metal/glass carport in front and back gazebo.

Welcome to this beautifully updated 2-bedroom, 1-bath coastal gem that feels much larger than its square footage suggests. Filled with natural light and featuring a thoughtfully open layout, the home offers a modern kitchen and cozy living spaces. Just steps from the beach and walking path, enjoy a peekaboo view of the bay and the beauty of Birch Bays tide flats, perfect for beachcombing and sunset strolls. Situated in a charming community, this home is ideal as a serene primary residence or an excellent short-term rental opportunity. Embrace the best of Birch Bay living!

Airy contemporary home with views and access to the gorgeous falls of Austin Creek, right outside your door. The main floor master suite is bright and spacious and the living room is HUGE! The layout boasts a modern kitchen that overlooks the living room area. Upstairs are two generous bedrooms and a bonus room that could be easily converted to a 4th bedroom. Enjoy access to all Sudden Valley amenities: Marina, Beaches, Parks, Clubhouse, Fitness Center, Pools & more!

Here we have a rare opportunity to own the ONLY vacant lot on Lake Whatcom. Boasting over 10, 000 sq/ft of flat, sunny land with 100 of lakefront, this is not one to miss! With city water & sewer already on site, you can begin enjoying your tranquil getaway on day one! This property has numerous sheds on site including one with power for convenient storing equipment or recreational gear. The large dock with covered boat lift makes summer lake days a blast! Moreover, the property's proximity to town offers the best of both worlds - the tranquility of lakeside living coupled with the convenience of urban amenities nearby. This blend of natural beauty and accessibility makes it an ideal location to fulfill the dream of building a custom home!

Welcome to Douglas Farm - a charming new community in Ferndale - close to Bellingham & the border! This beautiful Bedford plan w/high end features & smartly designed living spaces backs to the community park. The main floor features an inviting great room w/cozy FP & gourmet kitchen w/massive island, 5 burner gas cooktop, walk-in pantry & adjacent sunroom plus a powder room, pocket office & covered patio. Upstairs, you'll find a primary suite w/lavish bath, 2 secondary BRs, a spacious loft & utility rm. Extras include landscaping, irrigation, fencing, 9 ft ceilings, central heating/cooling, EV charging & more! If working w/a licensed broker, please register your broker on your 1st visit per our site reg policy. ASK ABOUT SPECIAL FINANCING!

Welcome to this charming updated 1930's farmhouse, nestled on just over an acre w/ stunning views of Mt. Baker & Wiser Lake. A gardener's paradise awaits, featuring fruit trees, raised beds, fire pit, horseshoe pit & mature landscaping. Exterior fully updated w/ new 50 yr architectural roof, Hardi siding & windows. Gorgeous original hardwood floors, custom concrete countertops & stainless appliances in the kitchen. Finished basement offers versatility including 2nd living room, flex space & an unfinished room that could be a 4th bedroom, plus ample storage, fresh paint & new LVP flooring throughout. The 26x40 shop is a dream w/ untapped potential upstairs, room for your toys/RV/boat, plus a new roof in 2019 and wood shed. Meridian schools!

Welcome to your new home in the heart of Bellingham! The nearby WWU makes this a tremendous opportunity. This move-in ready condo unit in the Puget neighborhood offers unparalleled convenience. Key features include its prime location; the second-floor unit just 500 feet from Whole Foods, Fred Meyer, public transit, Civic Field, Arne Hanna Aquatic Center, and trails. Inside, the unit boasts newer luxury vinyl plank flooring and all appliances, including a washer and dryer. This condo is not just a comfortable living space, but also a versatile investment opportunity. Whether you choose to make it your personal residence or a strategic investment, this charming condo is ready for you to make it your own.

This home is located in Fairhaven's Parkway Village 55 and better active community. If you have been looking for a community to connect w/ and experience all that South Bellingham has to offer, this is it! Come look at this 1498 sqft, 2 bdrm + a den and a sunroom, 2 bathroom single-level home with an attached carport and storage area. The kitchen is light and bright with a skylight, updated kitchen cabinets and a huge pantry. The interior living areas have been freshly painted and carpets are cleaned. Enjoy the fully fenced-in backyard with a patio, apple tree, grape vines, and a mature landscape. This home is move-in ready for you; don't miss out on the opportunity to call this home!

Rare opportunity to have a new home in the desirable Ridgemont neighborhood with Southside schools. This gorgeous home by Slusher Luxury Homes has an extensive list of upgrades that include a 8' island kitchen complete with Thermador commercial apps, quartz c/tops & huge pantry. The main floor of this contemporary designed home also has 9' ceilings on both floors, a 46 linear f/p, an open living & dining room concept, large study + separate den, custom mud room & is complete with engineered hardwood flooring. Upstairs enjoy a spacious primary bdrm & closet with 4 piece bath & huge flex space. This home is complete with a beautiful 22x28 covered patio with a huge panoramic sliding door, detailed T&G ceiling and built-in BBQ & 2 paddle fans!

This light-filled home on a quiet cul-de-sac is designed for the modern lifestyle and entertaining, with an open and flowing layout. The living/dining room flows into the spacious kitchen, which has extra counterspace, double ovens, gas stove and breakfast bar. Off the kitchen is a bonus room with cozy gas fireplace, and both the dining and bonus rooms have sliding doors onto an extra large, full length tropical hardwood deck. First floor bedroom could be a home office. Upstairs is the spacious master suite with walk-in closet and full bathroom. Heat pump, furnace and A/C are new in last few years. The home is on a shy quarter-acre that is fully fenced, with plenty of room to garden, and a storage shed. Easy access to Samish Crest trails.

Estate Sale. First time offered. Dream waterfront location on the enchanting west shore of Lummi Island. Majestic views of Georgia Strait and the stunning San Juan Islands. Easy access to the beach to watch Mother Nature's finest show. This 1866 sf home features 2 bedrooms and 2+ bathrooms. The large open main floor area has great flow for entertaining. Basement (480 sf) would make a nice art studio, rental or guestroom. Built in 1991, this home is ready for you to put your personality into it, and make it a spectacular showplace. The possibilities are endless. Bonus- there is a 1728 sf pole barn on this 2 acre property. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to embrace island life, and make your coastal living dreams come true!

text: Looking for the Bellingham Unicorn? This 4+ bedroom home in town with a large lot, privacy and only 5 minutes to shops/dining is it! Savor your morning coffee by the sunroom fireplace or on the 17x17 covered patio while you listen to the birds sing in the treetops. The main level has 2 bedrooms and a large living area that allows for a flexible configuration. The lower level has 2 bedrooms, full bath, add'l living space that can be an office, gym, or 5th bedroom as well as access to the yard and full 2 car garage. Dont miss the pet wash station and new AC unit.

Sunny 4-bed, 2.5-bath home invites you in with brand new hardwood floors and fresh paint throughout! Main floor features french doors leading to bright den/office/bed. One of the best slips in the Marina, easy docking and access to fuel dock, also well protected and close to shore. Great shore facilities, store, cafe, restrooms with clean showers, laundry and off street parking. Owners receive a discount at the fuel dock on gas or diesel. Great access to gulf islands in Canada or all the beautiful San Juan Islands, also good crabbing near by. Exceptionally well maintained marina you will enjoy.

Refined living. Nature at your door step. You'll be captivated by the walls of windows that fill the interior with natural light accentuating the beautiful finishes. Nestled near the Galbraith Trails, this home perfectly blends convenience with tranquility.

Your wait is over! Beautifully updated 3 bed 2 bath home, fully insulated shop (26'x36'), w/10'x26' loft, lg flex space (possible ADU?), 12' rollup door, & garden shed. Beautiful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom with 2, 625 sqft of comfortable living space. Kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets. Rare find-One of a kind Contemporary stick build (container style home) on wooded rare 2+ acres inside the city limits. Great opportunity to stop paying someone else's mortgage and get started in home ownership. Prime property to use as a stepping stone to your ultimate home. 950+ sq ft. 2 bed, 1 bath stick build home, on a corner lot. Amazing location right across the street from the city park which is a block from downtown. Fenced area for the pet. Easy maintained yard. No water damage from last years epic flooding.

Discover this beautifully updated 4-bedroom, 2.25-bath Ferndale gem!
